Uses of Package
de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes

  • Packages that use de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes 
    Package Description
    de.dfki.adom.rest
    Classes responsible for the handling of an object memory on the REST interface.
    de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes
    Components that represent nodes in the REST tree.
  • Classes in de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes used by de.dfki.adom.rest 
    Class and Description
    FeatureNegotiation
    A Component to handle the feature negotiation of an object memory via the REST interface.
    Management
    A Component to handle memory management via the REST interface.
    Storage
    A Component to handle the block storage of an object memory via the REST interface.
    Sync
    A Component to handle the sync properties of a memory via the REST interface.
  • Classes in de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes used by de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes 
    Class and Description
    Block
    A Component to handle the addition of OMM blocks to a memory via the REST interface.
    BlockIDs
    A Component to output all block IDs of a memory via the REST interface.
    BlockManager
    A Component to handle the retrieval of OMM blocks and block information via the REST interface.
    Component
    A blueprint offering basic functionality for nodes of the REST interface, like handling HTTP commands and issuing errors.
    MetaInfo
    A Component to handle the output of meta information about a block via the REST interface (in default format: XML).
    Payload
    A Component to handle interaction with a block's payload via the REST interface.
    SpecificBlock
    A Component to handle the output and deletion of specific OMM blocks via the REST interface.
    Toc
    A Component to provide a memory's Table of Contents via the REST interface.
